Today is the day, I'm packing my bags and leaving a city I've called home for six months. When I started this journey I was so excited to see places I've never even dreamed of, meeting people from all edges of the planet, and doing things I would've never imagined, but no one told me the hardest part is leaving it all behind. I think the most difficult thing about traveling from place to place is growing so close to people and then one day you have to pack it all up and go to the next. I've met so many incredible people, and became so close with so many of you, I don't even consider us friends, we are family. I thank each and everyone of you for the memories we share whatever they may be, I have so much love for all of you, I've never felt more home in a city in my entire life. Thank you Hong Kong for this amazing chapter in my life, I will never forget it. Even though I'm leaving I have a feeling that Hong Kong hasn't seen the last of meüòè Until we see each other again, my home kong‚ù§Ô∏è #Hongkong #homekong #muchlove #love #thefeels #modeling #travel #journey
